        {
            "type": "title",
            "source": "About this theme",
            "target": "关于此主题"
        },
        {
            "type": "description",
            "source": "This is a high-performance clone of the famous [AnuPpuccin](https://github.com/AnubisNekhet/AnuPpuccin) theme (GPL-3.0)",
            "target": "这是一个高性能的 [AnuPpuccin](https://github.com/AnubisNekhet/AnuPpuccin) 主题克隆版本 (GPL-3.0)"
        },
        {
            "type": "markdown",
            "source": "true",
            "target": "true"
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "source": "Extended Colorschemes",
            "target": "扩展配色方案"
        },
        {
            "type": "description",
            "source": "This theme supports the extended colorschemes from the AnuPpuccin theme. You can find the snippet here: [AnuPpuccin Themes Extended](https://github.com/AnubisNekhet/AnuPpuccin/blob/main/snippets/extended-colorschemes.css)",
            "target": "此主题支持 AnuPpuccin 主题的扩展配色方案。您可以在以下位置找到代码片段：[AnuPpuccin Themes Extended](https://github.com/AnubisNekhet/AnuPpuccin/blob/main/snippets/extended-colorschemes.css)"
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "source": "Rainbow Folders",
            "target": "彩虹文件夹"
        },
        {
            "type": "description",
            "source": "To use AnuPpuccin's Rainbow Folders, download the snippet from [here](https://github.com/LostViking09/obsidian-fastppuccin/blob/master/snippets/fastppuccin-rainbow-folders.css).\\nIt also supports [Custom Rainbow Colors](https://github.com/AnubisNekhet/AnuPpuccin/blob/main/snippets/custom-rainbow-colors.css) from AnuPpuccin.",
            "target": "要使用 AnuPpuccin 的彩虹文件夹功能，请从 [此处](https://github.com/LostViking09/obsidian-fastppuccin/blob/master/snippets/fastppuccin-rainbow-folders.css) 下载代码片段。\\n它还支持 AnuPpuccin 的 [自定义彩虹颜色](https://github.com/AnubisNekhet/AnuPpuccin/blob/main/snippets/custom-rainbow-colors.css)。"
        },
